metadata.name: bacchus
metadata.description:
bacchus is an incarnation to god of frenzies, festivities, spiritual ecstasy, wine, art and alcohol in general. bacchus love to do some party and dancing when welcoming anyone who already pass the angel and zealot trial.
bacchus live in second layer of heaven, he always had big shield that has double function, either its for protecting everyone who enter the heaven, he also using it as an music player and speaker at the same time.
